  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><math><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mn>9</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math></p><p>How many distinct real solutions are there to the given equation?</p>",
