  "rationale": "<p>For a quadratic ax\u00b2 + bx + c = 0, the number of real solutions is determined by the discriminant b\u00b2 \u2212 4ac. Here b\u00b2 \u2212 4ac = (\u22129)\u00b2 \u2212 4(2)(10) = 81 \u2212 80 = 1 > 0, so the equation has exactly two distinct real solutions.</p>",
